      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the iconic S54-powered platform. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a functional Double VANOS system, providing a broad powerband and exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings have been serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its communicative edge with refreshed bushings and dampers, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of an M-division product. While it shows honest wear from enthusiast use, the drivetrain and structural components are dialled in for peak performance.",
