      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained car that looks as good as it performs. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, with only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean; the seats show minimal bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by floor mats, and it has never been smoked in. All onboard technology, including the infotainment system and safety sensors, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no unusual noises, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. We have kept up with all scheduled maintenance, including recent fluid changes and a brake inspection. The tires are in great shape with plenty of miles left. This is a solid, honest car that delivers a premium driving experience and is ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
